title: Prep Zone picks: Week 8
text:
FOXSPORTS Prep Zone picks: Week 8 Check out the Week 8 Prep Zone picks from FOX Sports West's Mark Rogondino, Rahshaun Haylock and John Jackson. Oct 22, 2015 at 2:02p ET 0Shares 
What's football without a little friendly competition?! 
Each week, our CIF-SS football talent, Mark Rogondino , Rahshaun Haylock and John Jackson , will select the winners for the four Prep Zone games ... which can be seen on FOX Sports GO. 
Note: The televsion Game of the Week will not be contests selected. 
We will then tally the weekly results to then determine the season-long winner. 
At the end of the year, the winner will host a pizza party for the entire FOX Sports West/Prime Ticket office. 
Good luck fellas!
